{"tid":2094352,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個有愛心嘅韓團隊長","createTime":"2020-07-04T14:34:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-06T06:09:47.000Z","uid":152432,"like":26,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"e4ade2e251e4c702c2f0e92b23d253f47e99c29c","tid":2094352,"uid":152432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T14:34:26.000Z","msg":"被隊員稱本世紀最偉大嘅女性 Irene<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n1mjksm.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn1mjksm.gif&h=0e84cd34&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P0PwV0H.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP0PwV0H.gif&h=973fe1db&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/07/04/223315_190a317baf0bb9282f1f901a0ed24a2b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F07%2F04%2F223315_190a317baf0bb9282f1f901a0ed24a2b.gif&h=493c6369&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/07/04/223317_e08b6cfa3421c31088df15ebd401eb47.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F07%2F04%2F223317_e08b6cfa3421c31088df15ebd401eb47.gif&h=b7d04546&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/07/04/223318_7b930817ce3c28f5d9655353dd8441b4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F07%2F04%2F223318_7b930817ce3c28f5d9655353dd8441b4.gif&h=691db22b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/07/04/223319_a8106416344791f8647c33caf3a72970.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F07%2F04%2F223319_a8106416344791f8647c33caf3a72970.gif&h=e154850f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/07/04/223320_6b0a021eb60ff298a6b6496d77fb6345.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F07%2F04%2F223320_6b0a021eb60ff298a6b6496d77fb6345.gif&h=5ef04b14&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/07/04/223321_e1a6824559a0bb5a64d36402deada40b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F07%2F04%2F223321_e1a6824559a0bb5a64d36402deada40b.gif&h=9d121aba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d509b52816d91841b70d459dc3f833985843ad15","tid":2094352,"uid":152432,"like":31,"dislike":6,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T14:37:54.000Z","msg":"成員Irene也因為出眾的外貌，一直讓她受到網友的關注，但是隨著逐漸的了解，大眾也開始了解到Irene到底是多麼溫暖的一個人，近日就有粉絲整理了Irene過往的暖心事跡，讓很多路人粉瞬間入坑<br />\n<br />\n被Wendy稱為這世界上最偉大的女性的Irene，當成員們和工作人員一起去吃飯時，因為高額的飯錢而感到苦惱時，總會安靜的走向櫃檯拿出自己的卡並說著「請幫我們結帳吧！」霸氣的舉動也讓妹妹們為之傾倒！<br />\n<br />\n不只如此只要成員們提過在哪裡看到什麼漂亮的東西，或是說過自己想要什麼，Irene聽了之後總會默默記在心裡，之後便會買下給成員當作禮物。<br />\n像是之前瑟琪說過自己想要行李箱，Irene也是先記下之後買了送給瑟琪，知道Yeri喜歡打遊戲，白菜也是買了高價的專業電競耳機送給了Yeri。<br />\n<br />\n但是當成員們問Irene想要什麼東西時，她卻總是說沒有，因為她想要的東西她自己買就行了，她喜歡自己做選擇時的那種樂趣。<br />\n還有練習生時期因為妹妹們的家都住很遠，因此過生日的的時候很多妹妹並不能回家，為了想家的妹妹們，Irene會做海帶湯和準備生日餐為她們慶祝，而直到現在Irene還是會為生日的成員們做海帶湯。<br />\n<br />\n因為Joy、Yeri喜歡吃炸雞，明明自己不太能吃雞，但是為了做給她們吃，Irene最擅長的料理也變成了辣雞塊。<br />\n而忙內Yeri還是高中時，校服基本上都是Irene幫她燙的，還會配合放學時間做零食給Yeri吃，也難怪之前節目中Irene會說Yeri是她餵大的啊！<br />\n<br />\n除了細心的照顧成員，Irene也是非常真誠的對待身邊的所有的工作人員啊！<br />\n像是這次日本巡迴演唱會結束後，Irene則是準備了睡衣組送給了所有的伴舞們，伴舞們也紛紛上傳影片和照片稱讚「Irene最棒~」<br />\n<br />\n還有之前Irene的髮型師只是無意地跟Irene說一雙鞋子很漂亮，後來Irene便買了寄到髮型師的家裡，讓髮型師又驚喜又感動～白菜真的太暖太暖了！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SozkPnf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSozkPnf.jpg&h=a1ee585e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"23a2fa6c5fa4b2b7d23d9a828bc357198539bf59","tid":2094352,"uid":136738,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T14:38:19.000Z